The paper focuses on improving knowledge graph embedding, which is a task related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of constraints to improve the embeddings is a technique related to machine learning (cs.LG) and databases (cs.DB). Finally, the evaluation of the approach involves information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
